# jemdoc: menu{MENU}{projects.html}
= Projects

== Research Workflow Toolkit
A lightweight collection of scripts and templates for turning experiments,
notes, and figures into a static research website.

- Stack: Python, Make, jemdoc, MathJax.
- Status: template scaffold ready.
- Link: [/https://github.com/siegfriedguo/research-workflow GitHub repository].

== Model Evaluation Dashboard
A placeholder project for comparing model outputs, collecting error categories,
and summarizing qualitative findings.

- Stack: Python, TypeScript, SQLite.
- Focus: evaluation design, reproducible analysis, report generation.

== Numerical Notes
A small library of worked examples in optimization and numerical linear algebra.

- Includes LaTeX equations rendered by MathJax.
- Designed for teaching notes and self-contained tutorials.
